bb_paragraph\">5 resisting the invasion of alien spaceships to defend the last territories of the Earth</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">6.the sea supply task</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">7.lunch Aircraft carrier carrier!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We produced high-precision  heavy weapon models in software in this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At present, there are 10 types of aircraft platforms including helicopters, trainers, tankers, deflection gyroplanes, attack aircraft, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are already 11 aircraft platforms including aircraft carriers, destroyers, landing ships, cruisers, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We fight for hope,for freedom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Complete China Mission 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/955890/df43ee5f8d9fef0fa1ca4a8f9e2de2646a85914f.jpg"},{"name":"Complete China Mission 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/955890/326672f1e35d0e499d93346902a4d0041482af5b.jpg"},{"name":"Complete USA Mission 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/955890/7d7b093647ffd49a2f21a8878ce1f2bd6818333b.jpg"},{"name":"Complete USA Mission 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/955890/07c9bb86bfdd54d1a4e572fea60c603368fc2cd8.jpg"},{"name":"Complete Russia Mission 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/955890/71a8ede3b704b080708c06cacd333400e4373859.jpg"},{"name":"Complete Russia Mission 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/955890/23535cb77d512b0efe945cf0bd0d7762036efa8f.jpg"},{"name":"iron  intruder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/955890/9b51760d434af3bd7e6deb723d44cbe59a010d37.jpg"},{"name":"Dragon Hunter","path":"ht